= class Gtk::SourceStyle

== Object Hierarchy

* Object
  * GLib::Instantiatable
    * GLib::Object
      * Gtk::SourceStyle

== Instance Methods

--- background

    Gets the Background color.
     * Returns: Background color

--- background_set?

    Gets the value whether background color is set or not.
     * Returns: true if background color is set

--- bold?

    Gets the Bold.
     * Returns: Bold

--- bold_set?

    Gets the value whether bold attribute is set or not.
     * Returns: true if bold attribute is set

--- copy

     * Returns: self: ((*FIXME*))

--- foreground

    Gets the Foreground color.
     * Returns: Foreground color

--- foreground_set?

    Gets the value whether foreground color is set or not.
     * Returns: true if foreground color is set

--- italic?

    Gets the Italic.
     * Returns: Italic

--- italic_set?

    Gets the value whether italic attribute is set or not.
     * Returns: true if italic attribute is set

--- line_background

    Gets the Line background color.
     * Returns: Line background color

--- line_background_set?

    Gets the value whether line background color is set or not.
     * Returns: true if line background color is set

--- strikethrough?

    Gets the Strikethrough.
     * Returns: Strikethrough

--- strikethrough_set?

    Gets the value whether strikethrough attribute is set or not.
     * Returns: true if strikethrough attribute is set

--- underline?

    Gets the Underline.
     * Returns: Underline

--- underline_set?

    Gets the value whether underline attribute is set or not.
     * Returns: true if underline attribute is set

