    Italic

--- italic-set: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether italic attribute is set

--- line-background: String (Read/Write)

    Line background color

--- line-background-set: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether line background color is set

--- strikethrough: true or false (Read/Write)

    Strikethrough

--- strikethrough-set: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether strikethrough attribute is set

--- underline: true or false (Read/Write)

    Underline

--- underline-set: true or false (Read/Write)

    Whether underline attribute is set

